-- Ferrari's Alonso Wins Singapore Grand Prix; Webber Keeps Lead in Standing
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2010-09-26T14:03:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/ferrari-s-alonso-wins-singapore-grand-prix-webber-keeps-lead-in-standings.html
Fernando Alonso of Ferrari won
today’s Singapore Grand Prix, with Red Bull duo Sebastian Vettel
and Mark Webber second and third. Webber keeps the lead in the
Formula One drivers’ standings.  It was polesitter Alonso’s fourth win this season, the 25th
of his career, and his second at Singapore.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  